(firstQuint)Effects of NUTRIOSEFB Dietary Fiber Supplementation on Satiety, Body Fat, and Metabolic Syndrome in Overweight Adult Men.

 Previous trials of fiber supplementation have yielded equivocal results on body composition, satiety, and determinants of metabolic syndrome.

 This double-blind, randomized, placebo-controlled study was conducted to determine the effects of a proprietary soluble dextrin dietary fiber supplement (NUTRIOSE(R)) on these parameters in overweight males.

